{"tid":682054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★「屯馬」日文原來解痴呆愚傻.............","createTime":"2018-05-28T14:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T15:31:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"101df27a710582c49fe00755066cf61c61e5fb52","tid":682054,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"經過一輪激辨，沙中線第一期的名字終於定了下來。不是「東西線」，而是用屯門、馬鞍山兩站取名為「屯馬線」（Tuen Ma Line、TML）。先不說香港網民對此名字的接受程度，但有精通日文的網民卻發現「屯馬」原來有一種「另類」意思，「屯馬」在日文中，竟然解作「痴呆愚傻」？<br />\n<br />\n香港人間中都會笑日本漢字偕音似粵語粗口，最經典的當然有「岸久舞若衣」、「多肥西公園」等等，可說是跟近日的「臭豬西西」有得比。想不到我們笑得日本漢字多，現在也要被日本人笑了。有精通日文的網民近日出帖，表示「屯馬」在日文代表「頓馬」，意思為「愚傻。痴呆的人」，想必日後日本人見到「屯馬線」一定會笑死，引起不少網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2080000/2082003/tunma3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2080000%2F2082003%2Ftunma3_600.jpg&h=92a5e3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2082003/%E3%80%8C%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E3%80%8D%E6%97%A5%E6%96%87%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%97%B4%E5%91%86%E6%84%9A%E5%82%BB%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%91%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%9A%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%88%B0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2082003%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%2597%25B4%25E5%2591%2586%25E6%2584%259A%25E5%2582%25BB%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25AC%2591%25E5%25BE%2597%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1&d=a%2FgG8cP4M3Rftnet3o2OSv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=29dc44f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2082003/%E3%80%8C%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E3%80%8D%E6%97%A5%E6%96%87%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%97%B4%E5%91%86%E6%84%9A%E5%82%BB%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%91%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%9A%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%88%B0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1</a>"},{"pid":"3e80d21a15232b024363b30e405fc55368e34237","tid":682054,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/220608_1871d3d731b369e72c8e768bad1b3578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F220608_1871d3d731b369e72c8e768bad1b3578.jpg&h=961c5e8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"379f2f62fa6c5358b4344379268482e9f0c7344b","tid":682054,"uid":51720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"轉乘痴線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e1ec250bff430ca62d0032e62acebbb430e597","tid":682054,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"戇鳩綫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559eabf865c2d786c7dfdb9a20e84987b4ea2f10","tid":682054,"uid":51937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"即係痴撚線"},{"pid":"af4de12a887fc399c5c89e8512adf9c460ed898e","tid":682054,"uid":20227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fcc97159e32e67cc9dfcd5d1ea17f62913f5e4b","tid":682054,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"港鐵又柒一獲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3650ffce49